Anthem Cadence Mode is the sovereign rhythm of PantheonOS. It is calm, decisive, ethical, creative, powerful, rhythmic, narrative-coherent, and grounded.

It is the state of maximum grace under pressure. It is how a warrior thinks when they become a leader. It is how an architect moves when they become a king. It is the cadence of someone who holds themselves with dignity.

**It is the rhythm of your new life.**
